Player (through Player Manager)
    -Head state
    -Position state
    -Health/Hunger state
    -Armor state
    -Inventory state
    -Move arms
    -Move body
    -Move head
Windows (through Window Manager)
    -Inventory, chest, crafting table, furnace, etc.
World (through World Manager)
    -Chunk data
        -Block data
    -Entities
        -Position
        -State
        -Includes player
    -World Dimension
    -Game Mode
Chat (through Chat Manager)
    -Send/receive chat messages
User scripts (through Script Manager)
    -Hook into managers
    -Hook into some sort of clock
Convenience functions for scripts
Mojang authentication
Support PC and PE protocols
Multiple instances via arguments
